        <p class="ga-body" style="font-size: 1.45rem; line-height: 1.6; color: var(--ga-dark-text); margin: 0; font-weight: 300;">
          Enjoy free shipping across India for all orders of **₹1,499 and above**. For orders below ₹1,499, a flat shipping fee of ₹99 applies.
        </p>
