  <!-- Section 1: Eco-Friendly Packaging -->
  <div class="ga-shipping-split">
    <!-- Left Arched Image -->
    <div style="text-align: center;" class="ga-reveal">
      <div class="ga-arch-container" style="max-width: 100%;">
        <img class="ga-arch-top" src="{{ 'ghar-aangan-product-ghee.jpg' | asset_url }}" alt="Ghar Aangan Premium A2 Ghee Bottle" style="width: 100%; max-width: 380px; height: auto; display: block;" loading="lazy">
      </div>
    </div>
    <!-- Right Text Content -->
    <div class="ga-reveal" style="animation-delay: 0.1s;">
      <span class="ga-subtitle">SECURE & ECO-CONSCIOUS</span>
      <h2 class="ga-title" style="font-size: clamp(2.4rem, 4vw, 3.4rem); margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: 2rem; font-family: var(--ga-font-family-serif);">Fragile Glass Jar Protection</h2>
      <p class="ga-body" style="font-size: 1.55rem; line-height: 1.7; color: var(--ga-dark-text); font-weight: 300; margin-bottom: 2rem;">
        To preserve the rich aroma, texture, and nutritional profile of our wood-fired A2 Ghee, we store it exclusively in premium, food-grade glass jars. Glass prevents chemical leaching and maintains natural freshness.
      </p>
      <p class="ga-body" style="font-size: 1.55rem; line-height: 1.7; color: var(--ga-dark-text); font-weight: 300;">
        We take transit safety seriously. Each glass jar is encased in custom-molded, multi-layered 5-ply corrugated cardboard shells that absorb severe impacts. We are committed to minimizing environmental impact, which is why **our shipping kits are 100% plastic-free and fully recyclable**.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Section 2: Transit Quality & Temperature Guard -->
  <div class="ga-shipping-split ga-reverse">
    <!-- Left Text Content -->
    <div class="ga-shipping-text ga-reveal" style="animation-delay: 0.1s;">
      <span class="ga-subtitle">CLIMATE INDEPENDENT</span>
      <h2 class="ga-title" style="font-size: clamp(2.4rem, 4vw, 3.4rem); margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: 2rem; font-family: var(--ga-font-family-serif);">Premium Transit Quality Guard</h2>
      <p class="ga-body" style="font-size: 1.55rem; line-height: 1.7; color: var(--ga-dark-text); font-weight: 300; margin-bottom: 2rem;">
        Unlike industrial processed spreads, authentic Bilona Ghee has a complex molecular structure containing essential short and medium-chain fatty acids. This wood-fired churning makes it highly stable under different temperature changes.
      </p>
      <p class="ga-body" style="font-size: 1.55rem; line-height: 1.7; color: var(--ga-dark-text); font-weight: 300;">
        Whether traveling through cold northern hills or warm southern plains, your ghee will arrive perfectly fresh. Slight changes in consistency (melting or solidifying) are completely natural signs of pure, unadulterated ghee and do not affect its shelf-life or taste.
      </p>
    </div>
