    <div class="ga-faq-container">
      
      <!-- FAQ 1 -->
      <details class="ga-faq-details">
        <summary class="ga-faq-summary">
          <span>What happens if my glass jar breaks during transit?</span>
          <span class="ga-faq-icon">✦</span>
        </summary>
        <div class="ga-faq-content">
          <p class="ga-body" style="font-size: 1.5rem; line-height: 1.6; font-weight: 300; margin: 0; color: var(--ga-dark-text);">
            We offer a **100% Transit Guarantee**. While our custom 5-ply protective packaging prevents damage in 99.8% of cases, courier handling can occasionally be unpredictable. If your glass jar arrives broken or leaking, please email us at **support@gharaangan.com** or message us on WhatsApp within **48 hours of delivery** with a photo or video of the packaging and jar. We will dispatch a brand-new replacement immediately at no extra cost.
          </p>
        </div>
      </details>

      <!-- FAQ 2 -->
      <details class="ga-faq-details">
        <summary class="ga-faq-summary">
          <span>How can I track my shipment in real-time?</span>
          <span class="ga-faq-icon">✦</span>
