        <div class="ga-faq-content">
          <p class="ga-body" style="font-size: 1.5rem; line-height: 1.6; font-weight: 300; margin: 0; color: var(--ga-dark-text);">
            As soon as our warehouse team packages your jar and hands it over to our courier partner (typically within 24-48 hours of your order), you will receive a tracking link via email and WhatsApp. You can click the link to see real-time location updates, estimated arrival dates, and contact information for the local delivery executive.
          </p>
        </div>
      </details>

      <!-- FAQ 3 -->
      <details class="ga-faq-details">
        <summary class="ga-faq-summary">
          <span>Do you offer Cash on Delivery (COD)?</span>
          <span class="ga-faq-icon">✦</span>
        </summary>
        <div class="ga-faq-content">
          <p class="ga-body" style="font-size: 1.5rem; line-height: 1.6; font-weight: 300; margin: 0; color: var(--ga-dark-text);">
            Yes, Cash on Delivery is available for most pin codes across India. Standard shipping is free on COD orders valued above ₹1,499. For COD orders below ₹1,499, a flat shipping fee of ₹99 is charged at checkout. A small COD handling fee of ₹49 may apply.
          </p>
        </div>
      </details>

      <!-- FAQ 4 -->
      <details class="ga-faq-details">
        <summary class="ga-faq-summary">
          <span>Can I change my delivery address after placing an order?</span>
          <span class="ga-faq-icon">✦</span>
        </summary>
        <div class="ga-faq-content">
          <p class="ga-body" style="font-size: 1.5rem; line-height: 1.6; font-weight: 300; margin: 0; color: var(--ga-dark-text);">
            If you need to change your shipping address, please contact our support team on WhatsApp or call us immediately. We can update your shipping details as long as the package has not left our dispatch facility. Once standard transit has begun with the courier provider, redirecting a package is generally not possible.
          </p>
        </div>
      </details>

      <!-- FAQ 5 -->
      <details class="ga-faq-details">
        <summary class="ga-faq-summary">
          <span>Do you ship internationally?</span>
          <span class="ga-faq-icon">✦</span>
        </summary>
        <div class="ga-faq-content">
          <p class="ga-body" style="font-size: 1.5rem; line-height: 1.6; font-weight: 300; margin: 0; color: var(--ga-dark-text);">
            By default, checkout on our online store is limited to deliveries within India. However, we can arrange international shipping to selected countries (e.g. USA, UK, Canada, UAE) for custom commercial weights. Please reach out to us at **support@gharaangan.com** with your requirements and address, and we will get back to you with a custom shipping quotation.
          </p>
        </div>
      </details>

